rses to bring you closer to your goal.</span><br><span lang=en class="en trans"></span></p><p><span lang=de class=de>You will immerse yourself in the German language with this course and get a feeling for them that would otherwise only have native speakers.</span><br><span lang=en class="en trans"></span></p><p><span lang=de class=de>I only work with people who are willing to leave behind old ways of thinking and be part of the language learning revolution.</span><br><span lang=en class="en trans"></span></p><p><span lang=de class=de>If you are such a person, you will gain much from this course.
